Hidden services are websites only accessible to Tor users. These can be run from tails simply by typing in a SECRET ADDRESS 

just click on the links below or cut and paste into your browser

A good place to start is the Hidden Wiki

<http://kpvz7ki2v5agwt35.onion/wiki/index.php/Main_Page>

Using startpage for your ordinary world wide web searches? try the hidden site DuckDuckGo for added privacy

<http://3g2upl4pq6kufc4m.onion/>

**Note : Hidden sites have .onion in their address and often have a scramble of letters. The format is different to sites which begin with www.**

Wikipedia - .onion is a pseudo-top-level domain host suffix (similar in concept to such endings as .bitnet and .uucp used in earlier times) designating an anonymous hidden service

