The Hidden web is legal and full of information you wont find anywhere else. It has valuable privacy features which make tracing you even harder. Welcome to the OTHER SIDE OF THE INTERNET, the side your grandmother most probably didn't tell you about

Tails developers please consider displaying more information about .onion web sites with a clear link on the main page and on web browsers. Hidden services is a valuable part of Tor and I think under promoted by Tails at this point


